{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-markdown-page-js","path":"/guides/basics","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Shiren SFC Wiki | Zoiteki","docsLocation":"https://github.com/zoiteki/shiren-1/tree/main/content"}},"markdownRemark":{"fields":{"id":"a9308acb-4432-5dc8-a05c-8cace10899da","title":"Basics","slug":"/guides/basics"},"parent":{"relativePath":"guides/basics.md"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Basics","metaTitle":"Basics - Shiren 1 Wiki","metaDescription":"Basic Guides & Information for Shiren the Wanderer"},"html":"<h2 id=\"Controls\" style=\"position:relative;\">Controls<a href=\"#Controls\" aria-label=\"Controls permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.65 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 342px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/shiren-1/static/24d8fd9cf38aa85ed84484d4988a28b4/e2c15/sfc_controller.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 65.54054054054055%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Super Famicom Controller\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/shiren-1/static/24d8fd9cf38aa85ed84484d4988a28b4/e2c15/sfc_controller.png\"\n        srcset=\"/shiren-1/static/24d8fd9cf38aa85ed84484d4988a28b4/12f09/sfc_controller.png 148w,\n/shiren-1/static/24d8fd9cf38aa85ed84484d4988a28b4/e4a3f/sfc_controller.png 295w,\n/shiren-1/static/24d8fd9cf38aa85ed84484d4988a28b4/e2c15/sfc_controller.png 342w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 342px) 100vw, 342px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>D-Pad: Movement</li>\n<li>A: Attack</li>\n<li>B: Run, Trade Places with NPC</li>\n<li>Y: Turn w/o moving, (sorts inventory while in menu)</li>\n<li>X: Menu</li>\n<li>L: Fire equipped Arrows</li>\n<li>R: Force diagonal movement</li>\n<li>Select: Show Map</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"UI\" style=\"position:relative;\">UI<a href=\"#UI\" aria-label=\"UI permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.65 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 256px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/shiren-1/static/338475e62076329bc2c7a50ce420efe1/6f3f2/stats.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 87.83783783783784%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Shiren the Wanderer Screenshot\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/shiren-1/static/338475e62076329bc2c7a50ce420efe1/6f3f2/stats.png\"\n        srcset=\"/shiren-1/static/338475e62076329bc2c7a50ce420efe1/12f09/stats.png 148w,\n/shiren-1/static/338475e62076329bc2c7a50ce420efe1/6f3f2/stats.png 256w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 256px) 100vw, 256px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>F: The Floor you are on</li>\n<li>Lv: Shiren's Level</li>\n<li>HP: Hit Points</li>\n<li>G: Gitan: currency</li>\n<li>Tools: Shiren's Inventory</li>\n<li>Map: Toggles the Map Overlay</li>\n<li>Floor: Shows the item or trap underneath Shiren</li>\n<li>Quit: Suspend the Game (on next load it will bring you back to the exact spot)</li>\n<li>Top Floor: The furthest you've gotten on this save file</li>\n<li>Satiation: Satiation is hunger/fullness. If your Satiation reaches 0% you stop regenerating HP and\r\nstart taking damage per turn</li>\n<li>Sword Str.: The power of Shiren's Sword</li>\n<li>Strength: Shiren's Current / Max Strength</li>\n<li>Shield Str.: The power of Shiren's Shield</li>\n<li>EXP: Experience Points</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Shiren's Level, Current Strength, and Sword Strength determines his damage, and his Shield Strength\r\ndetermines the damage he receives from Monsters.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Items\" style=\"position:relative;\">Items<a href=\"#Items\" aria-label=\"Items permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.65 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p>Shiren does not have any innate abilities, he can move, attack, and use <a href=\"../items/\">items</a>. Other than\r\nequipment, all items have limited usage - Shiren is a game about managing your items!</p>\n<h3 id=\"Equipment\" style=\"position:relative;\">Equipment<a href=\"#Equipment\" aria-label=\"Equipment permalink\" class=\"custom-class after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.65 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p>Straightforward: <a href=\"../items/weapons\">Swords</a> increase Attack. <a href=\"../items/shields\">Shields</a> increase Defense.\r\n<a href=\"../items/bracers\">Bracers</a> give a passive effect. <a href=\"../items/arrows\">Arrows</a> can be fired with the L\r\nbutton or from the menu. You can only have one of each equipped.</p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#controls\">Controls</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#ui\">UI</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#items\">Items</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#equipment\">Equipment</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","headings":[{"id":"Controls","value":"Controls","depth":2},{"id":"UI","value":"UI","depth":2},{"id":"Items","value":"Items","depth":2},{"id":"Equipment","value":"Equipment","depth":3}]},"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/dungeons/feis-final-problem","title":"Feis Final Problem"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/dungeons/food-god","title":"Food God"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/dunge